hadiths[84]{hadithnumber,text}:
3242,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney (kisi haakim waghaira ki majlis mein mahboos ho kar ya deeda-daanista (jaan-boojhkar)) jhooti qasam khai to usey chahiye ke apney chehrey ka maqam aag mein bana ley.''"
3243,"Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood) (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney qasam khai aur wo is mein jhoota ho taake iskey zariey se kisi musalman ka maal maar ley , to wo Allah se milega jabke wo us par ghazabnaak hoga.'' Ash'as (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qasam ! ye hadees merey hi baarey mein hai. meri aur eik yahudi ki zameen mushtarak thi, wo merey hissey se inkari ho gaya to maine ye maamla Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke huzur pesh kiya. aapney mujh se puchha : ''kya tumharey gawah hain?'' maine kaha : nahin. to aapney yahudi se farmaya : ''qasam uthao.'' maine arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! wo to qasam utha lega aur mera maal maar lega . tab Allah taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaai : ( إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله وأيمانهم ثمنا قليلا . . ۔) ''jo log Allah ke ehad aur apni qasmon par maamuli maal hasil kartey hain unka aakhirat mein koi hissey nahin, Allah unki taraf nazar nahin farmaeyga aur na un se kalam kerega aur na unhen paak kerega aur unke liye dard naak azab hai.''"
3244,"Hazrat Ash'as bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke (qabeela) kanda aur hizre-maut ke do aadmi apni eik zameen ka tanaaza' lekar Nabi karim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur ye zameen Yamen mein thi. Hizrami ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! meri zameen is shakhs ke baap ne mujh se zabardasti chheen li thi aur ye ab iskey qabzey mein hai. aapney puchha : ''kya tumharey koi gawah hain?'' usney kaha : nahin. lekin main isey qasam deta hun ke (wo ye kahe) Allah ki qasam ! wo nahin janta ke wo zameen meri hai jo iskey baap ne mujh se zabardasti chheen li thi. udhar Kandi aadmi bhi qasam khaney ke liye tayyar ho gaya , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo koi qasam utha kar kisi ka maal maar leta hai to wo Allah se is haal mein milega ke kodhi hoga.'' chunanche Kandi ne kaha : ye zameen isi ki hai."
3245,"Janab Alqama bin Waael bin Hajar Hizri apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke hizre-maut aur (qabeela) kanda ke do aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaye to hizrami ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye shakhs merey baap ki zameen par qaabiz ho gaya hai. Kandi ne kaha : ye meri zameen hai, merey qabzey mein hai, main hi usey kaasht karta hun aur uska is mein koi haq nahin hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hizrami se kaha : ''kya terey paas gawah hain?'' usney kaha : nahin. aapney farmaya : '' to tumhen uski qasam qubul kerni hogi.'' usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye faajir aadmi hai, isey koi parwa nahin ke kya qasam kha raha hai, ye kisi cheez se parhez nahin karta , to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumharey liye uski taraf se bas yehi hai (ke wo qasam khaye).''  chunanche wo qasam khaney ke liye tayyar ho gaya. jab usney pusht pheri to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar usney qasam kha li ke zulm se maal kha ley to ye Allah se milega is haal mein ke wo is se rukh pherey huey hoga.''"
3246,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis kisi ne merey is member ke paas jhooti qasam khai , chahey (chahe) eik (taza) miswak hi par kyon na ho, usney apna thikana jahannam mein bana liya.'' ya farmaya : ''uskey liye jahannam wajib hai.''"
3247,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney qasam khai aur apni qasam mein yun kaha : qasam hai laat ki ! to usey chahiye ke kahe : (La-ilaah-illallah). aur jisney apney sathi se kaha : aao jua khelein ! to usey chahiye ke kuchh sadqa karey.''"
3248,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney baapon ya maaon ke naam ki qasmen na khaya karo aur na buton ke naam ki . sirf Allah ke naam ki qasam khaya karo, aur Allah ki qasam bhi usi soorat mein khao jab tum sachchey ho.''"
3249,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke wo eik qafiley mein ja rahey they ke peechhey se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unhen aan miley. (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko suna) jabke wo apney baap ki qasam kha rahey they, to farmaya : ''Allah taala tumhen mana farmata hai ke apney baap aur daadaon ki qasmen khao , jisey qasam khaani ho wo Allah ke naam ki qasam khaye , ya khamosh rahey.''"
3250,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se suna (ke main apney baap ke naam ki qasam kha raha tha) mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne mazeed kaha : Allah ki qasam ! (baad iske) maine unki qasam nahin khai , na jaanbujhkar aur na hikayatan (kisi ki taraf se naqal kartey huey)."
3251,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kisi ko suna ke wo Kaaba ki qasam kha raha tha to unhoney us se kaha : beshak maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna hai : ''jisney ghairullah ki qasam khai usney shirk kiya.''
3252,"Janab Talha bin Ubaidullah ne badwi ke waqiey wali hadees mein bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kamiyab hua , qasam uskey baap ki ! agar sachcha (Sabit qadam) raha. jannat mein dakhil hua , qasam uskey baap ki ! agar ye sachcha (Sabit qadam ( raha.''"
3253,"Janab (Sulaiman) ibne Barida apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney amanat ki qasam khai , wo ham mein se nahin.''"
3254,"Janab Ata (Rahimahullah) se fuzul aur bekar qasam ke baarey mein marwi (bayan) hai, unhoney kaha, Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''is se murad wo qasam hai jo aadmi apney ghar mein (كلا والله) ! aur (بلى والله !) ( nahin, qasam Allah ki ! haan qasam Allah ki ! ( waghaira boltaa rehta hai.'' (us ka takiya kalam hota hai aur qasam ka qasad (irada) nahin hota.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Ibrahim Saaigh eik saleh aadmi they. unko Abu-Muslim ne maqame-arandas mein qatl kar diya tha. aur unka ye mamool tha ke agar hathodaa uthaya hua hota aur Azan sun letey to wahin chhod detey they. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : is hadees ko Daadoo bin Abi Faraat ne ba-waaste Ibrahim Saaigh, Hazrat Aaysha par moquf riwayat kiya hai aur aisey hi Zohri , Abdul-Malik bin Abi Sulaiman aur Malik bin Mighwal ne ba-waaste Ata , Hazrat Aaysha se moquf riwayat kiya hai."
3255,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teri qasam usi baat par hai jis par tera sathi tujh se tasdeeq kara raha hai. Janab Musaddad (Rahimahullah) ne is sanad mein (عن (an) Ibaad bin Abi Saleh) ke bajaey ( (''Akhbirni Abdullah bin Ubai saleh'') kaha hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ye dono Abdullah bin Ubai Saleh aur Ibaad bin Abi Saleh eik hi shakhsiyat hain."
3256,"Hazrat Suwaid bin Hanzala (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaney ki niyat se rawana huey aur hamarey sath Waael bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. unke eik dushman ne unko pakad liya , to qom ke log qasam khaney se hichkichaatey rahey, magar maine qasam kha li ke ''ye mera bhai hai.'' to usney isey chhod diya. phir ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur maine aap ko bataya ke qom ke logon ne qasam khaney mein harj samjha tha, magar maine qasam khai ke ''ye mera bhai hai, to aapney farmaya : ''tu ne sach kaha, musalman musalman ka bhai hota hai.''"
3257,"Hazrat Sabit bin Suhaak (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath ( Hudebiya mein) darkht ke nichey baiat ki thi. beshak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney millate Islam ke siwa kisi aur millat mein ho janey ki qasam khai chahey (chahe) wo jhoota hi kyon na ho, to wo usi tarah hai jaisa ke usney kaha. aur jisney jis chiz se apney aap ko qatl kya usey qiyamat ke din usi se azab diya jaeyga. aur jo cheez insan ki apni milkiyat mein na ho, uski nazar bhi nahin hai.''"
3258,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Barida apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney qasam khai ke main Islam se bari hun, to agar wo jhoota hua to wo wohi hua jo usney kaha aur agar sacha bhi hua to Islam ki taraf sahih Salim nahin lautey ga.''"
3259,Hazrat Yusuf bin Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aapney eik khajoor roti ke tukdey par rakhi aur farmaya : ''ye iska salan hai.''
3260,Yazid Aa'war ne Hazrat Yusuf bin Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) se uskey misl (jaisi) riwayat kiya.
3261,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf nisbat kartey huey bayan kartey hain : ''jisney qasam khai aur phir (inshaAllah) keh diya to usney istasna kar liya.''"
3262,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney qasam khai aur (inshaAllah) kaha to chahey wo apni qasam ko pura karey ya na karey, qasam nahin tutegi."
3263,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aksar qasmen is tarah ki hoti thin : لا،‏‏‏‏ ومقلب القلوب ''nahin, qasam hai us zaat ki jo dilon ka pherney wala hai.''"
3264,Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab bahut taakidi qasam khatey to yun kaha kartey they : والذي نفس أبي القاسم بيده ''qasam hai us zaat ki jiskey haath mein abul-Qaasim ki jaan hai! ''
3265,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab qasam khatey to yun kaha kartey : لا،‏‏‏ وأستغفر الله ''nahin! aur main Allah se bakhshish chahta hun.''
3266,"Aasim bin Laqeet kehtey hain ke Hazrat Laqeet bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) eik wafad ley ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye. Laqeet kehtey hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. aur is silsiley mein hadees zikr ki, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''terey Ilaah ki baqaa ki qasam .''"
3267,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko qasam di to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qasam mat do.'' ( tafsil nichey likhi riwayat mein hai. (
3268,"Janab ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey they ke eik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : beshak maine aaj raat khuwab dekha hai aur phir usney apna khuwab bayan kya. aur phir Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne uski tabeer ki, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne kuch mein durust kaha hai aur kuch mein khata ki hai.'' to unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool! main aap ko qasam deta hun, mera baap aap par fidaa ho! aap mujhey zarur bataiye ke maine kya ghalati ki hai, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se farmaya : '' qasam mat do.''"
3269,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye hadees bayan ki magar us mein qasm ka zikr nahin hai. aur us mein mazeed ye hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen wazahat nahin ki .
3270,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin abi Bakr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke hamarey yahan kuch mehman aa gaey, jabkey Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) raat ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath guftgu mein mashghool ho jaya kartey they. to unhoney kaha ke merey aaney tak tum unki ziyaafat aur khidmat se farigh ho jana. chunanche main unke paas unki ziyaafat lekar aaya to unhoney kaha : ham nahin khaeyngey yahan tak ke abu-Bakar aa jaeyn. chunanche wo (der sey) aaye aur puchha ke tumharey mehmano ka kya hua , kya tum unki mahmaandari se farigh ho chukey ho? ghar walon ne kaha : nahin. maine arz kya ke main unke paas unki ziyaafat ley gaya tha magar unhoney inkar kar diya aur kaha : Allah ki qasam! ham nahin khaeyngey yahan tak ke abu-Bakar aa jaeyn. un mehmano ne bhi tasdeeq ki ke ye hamarey paas ziyaafat laya tha magar ham ne inkar kar diya yahan tak ke aap aa jaeyn. abu-Bakar ne puchha : tumhen (merey baghair) khaney se kya maane (rukawat) raha? unhoney kaha : aap ke baais. (aap ki ghair mojudgi). to abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : qasam Allah ki ! main aaj raat ye nahin khaaunga. to unhoney kaha : aur ham bhi Allah ki qasam nahin khaeyngey yahan tak ke aap khaeyn. abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aaj jaisi buri raat maine nahin dekhi aur farmaya : khana lao. chunanche unka khana pesh kya gaya to kaha : Bismillah aur khaney lagey aur mehmano ne bhi khaya. (Abdur-Rehman kehtey hain) mujhey bataya gaya ke subh ke waqt wo (abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur wo sab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kaha jo kuch unhon (abu-Bakar ( ne kya aur mehmano ne kya. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum un se badh kar saleh ho aur sachey bhi .) ke mehmano ke ikram mein unki qasm ke mutabiq khana kha liya.'' ("
3271,abu-Usman ne Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin abi Bakr se ye hadees mazkura baala hadees ki manind riwayat ki. aur ibn Musanna ne Salim ki is hadees mein mazeed kaha : mujhey ye baat nahin pahunchi ke (Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( kaffara bhi diya.
3272,"Janab Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahimahullah) se riwayat hai ke Ansariyon mein do bhaiyon mein virasat ka maamla tha. eik ne doosrey se taqseem ka mutalba kya to usney kaha : agar to ne mujh se dobara taqseem ki baat ki to mera sab maal Kaaba ke liye waqf hua. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se farmaya : Kaaba terey maal ka mohtaj nahin. apni qasm ka kaffara ada kar aur apney bhai se (taqseem ke baarey mein) baat kar. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap farmatey they : ''rab taala ki nafarmani mein teri koi qasm hai, na nazar aur na qata-rehmi mein nazar hai aur na us chiz mein jiska to Malik nahin.''"
3273,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid sey, wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' koi nazar nahin siwaye uskey jis mein Allah ki raza maqsood ho aur na qata' rehmi mein qasam hai.''"
3274,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid sey, wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ibne-Adam jis chiz ka Malik na ho us mein nazar nahin aur na us mein qasam hai aur na Allah ki nafarmani mein aur na qata talluqi mein. aur jisney qasam khai ho aur phir uskey khilaf doosrey pehlu mein ziyada khair dekhay to chahiye ke qasam chhod dey aur jo khair ho us par amal karey. bila-shuba uska chhod dena hi uska kaffara hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sab ahadis mein yehi hai ke qasm ka kaffara ada karey, magar un riwayaat mein (uskey bar-aks bayan hua hai) jinka koi aetbar nahin. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : maine Imam Ahmed (Rahimahullah) se poochha, kya Yahya bin Saeed ne Yahya bin Ubaidullah se riwayat kya hai? to unhoney kaha ke baad mein chhod diya tha aur wo usi laaiq tha. aur Imam Ahmed (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : uski ahadis had se zyada zaeef hain aur uska baap ghair maroof hai."
3275,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke do shakhs apna jhagda Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas lekar aaye, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne muddai se gawah talab kiye to uskey paas gawah nahin they. tab aapney muddua aleh se qasam talab ki to usney kaha : ''qasam hai Allah ki jiskey siwa koi mabud nahin! (maine ye kaam nahin kya hai jo muddai kehta hai.) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kyon nahin, beshak to ne ye kya hai, lekin Allah ne tujhey ikhlas ke sath ( La-ilaa-h-illallah) kehney ki wajeh se bakhsh diya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain us se murad ye hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey (jhuti qasam khaney par) kaffara ada kerney ka hukm nahin diya."
3276,"Hazrat abu-Barda apney walid (Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki qasam! agar main koi qasam khaaun aur phir uskey khilaf ko behtar paun to bil-zaroor insha Allah apni qasm ka kaffara ada kar dunga aur wohi karunga jo behtar hoga.'' ya yun farmaya : (إلا أتيت الذي هو خير و كفرت يميني) ''magar main wo karunga jo behtar hoga aur apni qasm ka kaffara de-dunga.''"
3277,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai kehtey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : ''aey Abdur-Rehman bin Samra! jab tum koi qasam khao, phir uskey khilaf ko usse behtar pao to wohi karo jo behtar ho aur apni qasm ka kaffara de-do. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : maine Imam Ahmed (Rahimahullah) se suna ke wo qasam todney se pehley kaffara ada kerney ki rukhsat detey they."
3278,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se mazkura baala hadees ki manind marwi (bayan) hai, magar us riwayat mein) ye izafa ( hai : '' apni qasm ka kaffara ada kar aur phir us par amal kar jo behtar ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke us baarey mein Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari , Hazrat Adi bin Hatim aur Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) se ahadis aai hain. kuch mein hai ke pehley khilafe-qasam amal karey phir kaffara dey aur kuch mein hai ke pehley kaffara dey aur phir khilafe-qasam amal karey."
3279,"Janab Abdur-Rehman bin hurmala, Umme-Habib binte-zuweb bin Qais Muzniya se riwayat kartey hain. . . . aur ye Umme- Habib pehley bano Aslam ke eik shakhs ki zojiyat mein thin . uskey baad ummul-momenin Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anha) ke bhatijey ke nikah mein ayen . . . . ibne-hurmala ne kaha : Umme- Habib ne hamen eik pemana saa hadiya diya aur bataya ke uskey shohar ( ummul-momenin Safiya (Raziallahu anha) ke bhatijey) ne Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anha) se naqal kya ke ye saa Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka tha. ( raawi hadees) Janab Anas bin Ayaz kehtey hain ke phir maine us saa ko maapa to (us daur ke umwi pemaney) Hisham bin Abdul-Malik bin Marwan ke pemaney ke mutabiq udhai mud ke barabar paya ."
3280,Muhammad bin Muhammad b-n khallad abu-Umar ka bayan hai ke hamarey paas eik mud tha jo Khalid (qasri) ki taraf mansoob tha jo Harun ke kaleja (eik pemane) se do gunaa tha. Muhammad bin Muhammad ne kaha : Khalid ke saa (mud) se Hisham bin Abdul-Malik ka saa murad hai.
3281,"Muhammad bin Muhammad bin khallad abu-Umar ne kaha : hamen Musaddad ne Umayya bin Khalid se bayan kya ke jab Khalid al-Qasri governer bana to usney saa ko do gunaa kar diya aur phir eik saa sola ratl ka ho gaya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) bayan farmatey hain ke Muhammad bin Muhammad bin khallad ko zangi ( siyah faam ( logon ne baandh kar qatl kya tha aur apney haathon se yun ishara kya, Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne apney haathon ko phelaya aur apni hatheliyon ko zameen ki taraf kya. kaha ke maine usey khuwab mein dekha aur us se puchha ke Allah ne tum se kya maamla kya? to unhoney kaha : mujhey jannat mein dakhil kar diya hai. maine kaha : to tumhen waqf ne koi zarar nahin diya! (zangiyon ke samney be dast w pa ho janey se tumhen koi nuqsan nahin pahuncha balke Allah ke yahan tumhara maamla saaf hi raha.)"
3282,"Hazrat Muawiya bin Hakam Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool! maine apni londi ko thappad maara hai. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey merey liye bahut bura qarar diya. maine arz kya : kya main usey azad na kar dun? aapney farmaya : ''usey merey paas lao.'' main usey aapki khidmat mein ley aaya. aapney us se daryaft farmaya : ''Allah kahan hai? '' usney kaha : aasman par . aapney puchha : ''main kon hun?'' usney kaha : aap Allah ke Rasool hain. aapney farmaya : ''usey azad kar do bila-shuba ye momin hai.''"
3283,"Janab shareed bin suwed Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke unki walida ne unko wasiyat ki ke wo uski taraf se eik emandar (londi ya ghulam) ki gardan azad kar den. chunanche wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool! meri walida ne wasiyat ki hai ke main uski taraf se eik momin gardan azad kar dun, to merey paas noobi qabiley ki siyah rang londi hai aur mazkura baala hadees ki manind riwayat kya. to kya main usey azad kar dun? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey merey paas bulao. chunanche usey bulaya to wo aai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usse puchha : ''tera rab kon hai? '' usney kaha : Allah . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puchha : ''main kon hun?'' usney kaha : Rasulullah . aapney farmaya : ''usko azad kar do, bila-shuba ye momin hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain (doosri sanad mein) Khalid bin Abdullah ne usey mursal bayan kya hai aur shareed ka zikr nahin kya."
3284,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs eik siyah rang londi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein laya aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! merey zimmey eik momin gardan azad karna hai, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us (londi) se daryaft farmaya : ''Allah kahan hai? '' usney ungli ke isharay se kaha ke aasman par hai. phir aapney puchha : ''main kon hun?'' to usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aasman ki taraf isharay se samjhaya ke aap Allah ke Rasool hain. to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey azad kar do beshak ye momin hai.''"
3285,"Janab Ikrima se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki qasam! main Quraish par zarur chadhai karunga . Allah ki qasam ! main Quraish par zarur chadhai karunga .'' Allah ki qasam ! main Quraish par zarur chadhai karunga . phir farmaya : ''insha Allah (agar Allah ne chaha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : is hadees ko kaee eik ne shareek sey, unhoney samaak sey, usney Ikrima sey, usney ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) sey, usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se musnad riwayat kya hai. Waleed bin Muslim ne shareek se riwayat mein kaha hai : ''phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un par chadhai nahin ki.''"
3286,"Janab Ikrima (Rahimahullah) marfooan bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki qasam ! main Quraish par zarur chadhai karunga . phir farmaya : '' (inshaAllah) agar Allah ne chaha .'' phir aapney kaha : ''Allah ki qasam ! main Quraish par zarur chadhai karunga (inshaAllah) aapney phir kaha : ''Allah ki qasam ! main Quraish par zarur chadhai karunga .'' phir khamosh rahey baad mein farmaya : '' (inshaAllah) agar Allah ne chaha . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke us riwayat mein Waleed bin Muslim ne shareek se mazeed ye bhi bayan kya : '' phir aapney un par chadhai nahin ki .''"
3287,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke (eik moqe par) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) nazar manney se mana farmaney lagey , aap farmatey they : '' nazar kisi chiz ko radd nahin karti balke uskey zariey se bakheel aadmi se maal nikala jata hai. Musaddad ne yun bayan kya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : '' beshak nazar kisi chiz ko radd nahin karti .''"
3288,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' (Allah taala ka irshad hai ke) nazar ibne-Adam ki taqdir mein, jisey maine pehley se muqaddar na kya ho, koi tabdeeli nahin laati, balke ye taqdir hi mein se hota hai ke insan nazar maan leta hai jiskey zariey se bakheel se kuch nikala jata hai aur wo kuch karwaya jata hai jo wo us se pehley nahin kar raha hota .''"
3289,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney Allah ki itaat ki nazar maani ho usey chahiye ke) usey pura kartey huey ( Allah ki itaat karey, aur jisney Allah ki masiyat aur nafarmani ki nazar maani ho wo uski nafarmani na karey. (aur nazar ko chhod dey.'' ("
3290,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki nafarmani mein koi nazar nahin aur uska kaffara qasam wala kaffara hai.''"
3291,"Ibne-Wahab ne ba-waaste Yunus , ibne-Shahab Zohri se mazkura baala sanad se usi ke ham-maani riwayat kiya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : maine Ahmed bin Sahbuyya se suna, wo kehtey they ke ibne Mubarak ne is hadees mein kaha hai : (حدث ابوسلمة) ''yani Abu-Salma ne hadees bayan ki ''ye Aslamiya bayan daleel hai ke Zohri ne usey Abu-Salma se barahe-rast nahin suna hai. aur Ahmed bin Muhammad (Marwazi) ne kaha : iski daleel wo riwayat hai jo hamein Ayub bin Sulaiman ne bayan ki hai. (nichey likhi riwayat : 3292 mein iski sanad aa rahi hai aur us mein ibne-Shahab Zohri aur Abu-Salma ke beech do wastey hain jo is sanad mein nahin hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke maine Imam Ahmed bin Hanbal (Rahimahullah) se suna, wo kehtey they ke logon ne ham par ye hadees khalat kar di hai. un se kaha gaya : kya iska fasad aap ke nazdik Sabit hai? aur kya Abu-Bakar bin Abi Ovais ke alawa kisi aur ne bhi isey riwayat kiya hai? unhoney kaha : Ayub bin Sulaiman bin Bilal is (Abu-Bakar bin Abi Ovais) se behtar tha aur Ayub ne isey riwayat kiya hai. jiski sanad nichey likhi hai.)"
3292,"Ahmed bin Muhammad Marwazi ne bayan kiya ke ham se Ayub bin Sulaiman ne bayan kiya Abu-Bakar bin Abi Ovais sey, unhoney Sulaiman bin Bilal sey, unhoney ibne-Abi Ateeq aur Musa bin Aqba sey, ( dono ne ( ibne-Shahab Zohri sey, unhoney Sulaiman bin Arqam se riwayat kiya hai ke Yahya bin Abi Kaseer ne unko khabar di Abu-Salma sey, unhoney Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey, wo kehti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ma'siyat (nafarmani) mein koi nazar nahin aur uska kaffara qasam wala hai. Ahmed bin Muhammad Marwazi ne kaha : asal mein hadees ki sanad yun hai, Ali bin Mubarak , Yahya bin Abi Kaseer sey, wo Muhammad bin Zuber sey, wo apney walid sey, wo Imran bin Husain sey, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se. Marwazi ka maqsad ye hai ke Sulaiman bin Arqam ko ismein weham hua hai. Zohri ne isse riwayat kartey huey (do wastey chhod diye aur) isey Abu-Salma sey, unhoney Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se mursal kar diya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke baqiya ne Auzaai sey, unhoney Yahya sey, unhoney Muhammad bin Zuber se Ali bin Mubarak ki sanad se usi ke misl (jaisi) bayan ki."
3293,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se apni behan ke mutalliq daryaft kiya, jisney ye nazar maani thi ke nangey paon aur nangey sar hajj karegi , to aapney farmaya : ''usey hukm do ke sar par kapda ley aur sawari par Sawar ho aur teen din ke rozey rakhey .''"
3294,"Ibne Juraij kehtey hain ke Yahya bin Saeed ne mujhey likha ke mujhey Ubaidullah bin Zahar, maula bani Zamra ne likha . . . . aur kya khoob aadmi tha. . . . ke Abu-Saeed Ruaini ne usey khabar di aur mazkura  Yahya ki sanadon se riwayat kiya aur usi ke ham-maani bayan kiya."
3295,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! meri behan ne nazar maani hai ke paidal hajj karey, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala teri behan ke mashaqqat uthaney se kuchh nahin kerega, (usey koi faeyda nahin hoga) usey chahiye ke Sawar ho kar hajj karey aur apni qasam ka kaffara dey.''"
3296,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Rahimahullah) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ki behan ne nazar maani ke Baitullah ko paidal hi jaeygi. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey hukm farmaya ke Sawar ho aur qurbani karey.
3297,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jab ye baat pahunchi ke Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ki behan ne paidal hajj kerney ki nazar maani hai, to aapney farmaya : ''bila-shuba Allah taala uski nazar se be-parwa hai, usey hukm do ke Sawar ho jaey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke isey Saeed bin Abi Aruba ne usi ki manind riwayat kiya hai, isliye Khalid ne bhi b-waaste Ikrima Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se usi ki manind bayan kiya hai."
3298,Janab Ikrima (Rahimahullah) se manqul hai ke Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ki behan (ne nazar maani ( jaisey ke Hisham ne riwayat kiya. magar us mein qurbani ka zikr nahin balke ye hai ke aapney farmaya : ''apni behan ko hukm do ke wo Sawar ho jaey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke isey Khalid ne Ikrima se riwayat kiya aur Hisham ki riwayat ke ham-maani bayan kiya.
3299,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke meri behan ne nazar maan li ke Baitullah ko paidal jaeygi . phir usney mujh se kaha ke iskey baarey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se daryaft karun. chunanche maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se maloom kiya to aapney farmaya : ''usey chahiye ke paidal chaley aur sawar bhi ho ley.''"
3300,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khutba irshad farma rahey they. aapney dekha ke eik aadmi dhoop mein khada hai. aapney uskey mutalliq daryaft kiya, to logon ne kaha : ye Abu Israeel hai. usney nazar maani hai ke khada hi rahega , baithey ga nahin, na saya hasil kerega aur na baat cheet kerega aur roza rakhega . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey kaho ke baat cheet karey, saya hasil karey aur baith jaey aur apna roza pura karey.''"
3301,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi ko dekha ke wo apney do beton ke darmiyan unke saharey ( mashaqqat ( se chal raha hai. aapney uskey mutalliq puchha to logon ne kaha ke usney paidal chalney ki nazar maani hai. to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba Allah taala uskey apney aap ko azab deney se be-parwa hai.'' aur usey hukm diya ke ''Sawar ho jaey''. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is riwayat ko Amr bin Abi Amr ne ba-waaste Aaraj , Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se iski manind riwayat kiya hai."
3302,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Baitullah ka tawaf kar rahey they. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik aadmi ke paas se guzrey ke doosra usey nakel dal kar liye ja raha tha to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski nakel ko apney haath se tod dala aur usey hukm diya ke uska haath pakad kar chaley.
3303,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ki behan ne nazar maani ke paidal hajj karegi , aur is mein uski himmat nahin thi. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba Shan wala Allah teri behan ke paidal chalney se be parwa hai, usey chahiye ke Sawar ho aur eik oontni qurbani dey.''"
3304,Janab Ikrima (Rahimahullah) se manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kaha : beshak meri behan ne nazar maani hai ke Baitullah ki taraf paidal chaleygi . to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba Allah taala teri behan ke Baitullah ki taraf paidal chalney se kuchh nahin kerega.'' ( Allah ko koi fayda hasil nahin hoga.)
3305,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Fateh Makka waley din eik aadmi khada hua aur kehney laga : aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine Allah ke liye nazar maani hai ke agar Allah ne aap ko Makka Fateh kara diya to main baitul-Maqdis mein do rakaat Namaz padhunga . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''yahin (Baitullah Al haram mein) padh lo.'' usney apni baat dohraee to aapney farmaya : ''yahin padh lo.'' usney apni baat teesri baar dohraee to aapney farmaya : ''tab teri marzi hai.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uskey misl (jaise) marwi (bayan) hai.
3306,Janab umr bin Abdur-Rehman bin Auf ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke kaee eik Sahaba se ye khabar riwayat ki hai aur ismein izafa hai ke phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qasam us zaat ki jisney Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko haq ke sath mab'oos kiya (bheja) hai ! agar to yahan Namaz padh leta to ye teri baitul-Maqdis mein Namaz padhney se kifaayat kar jata . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : is riwayat ko (Muhammad bin Abdullah bin Musanna ( Ansari ne ibne-Juraij se riwayat kiya to (sanad ke raawiyon mein Hafs bin umr ki bajaey ( Jaafar bin Amr kaha : aur aisey hi ( Amr bin Hana ki bajaey ( Amr bin Haiyya kaha : ( yaa ke sath (aur kaha ke in dono ne Abdur-Rehman bin Auf aur deegar kaee Sahaba se riwayat kiya.
3307,"Hazrat Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha aur kaha ke meri walida faut ho gaee hai aur uskey zimmey nazar thi jo wo puri nahin kar saki , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum uski taraf se puri kar do.''"
3308,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke eik aurat samandari safar mein gaee to usney nazar maani ke agar Allah ne usey najat de-di to wo eik mahina rozey rakhey gi . chunanche Allah ne usey najat de-di , magar usney rozey na rakhey yahan tak ke mar gaee . isliye uski beti ya behan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai to aapney usey hukm diya ke wo uski taraf se rozey rakh ley."
3309,Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aurat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai aur kaha : maine apni walida ko eik londi sadqa ( Atiya ( ki thi aur ab wo ( walida ( faut ho gaee hai aur londi tarkey mein chhod gaee hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tera sawab Sabit hua aur wo londi virasat mein tujhey dobara mil gaee.'' usney bataya ke walida ke zimmey eik mahiney ke rozey bhi hain. aagey mazkura baala hadees Amr bin Auf ki manind bayan ki.
3310,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai ke eik aurat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aai aur kaha : beshak meri walida ke zimmey eik mahiney ke rozey they to kya main uski taraf se qaza kar sakti hun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar teri walida par qarza hota to kya to usey ada karti ?'' usney kaha : haan . aapney farmaya : '' tu Allah ka qarza ziyada aham hai ke usey ada kya jaey.''
3311,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo faut ho jaey aur uskey zimmey rozey hon to uska wali) waris ( uski taraf se rozey rakhey.''"
3312,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid sey, wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke eik aurat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai aur kehney lagi : aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine nazar maan rakhi hai ke main aap ke sar ke paas daf bajaaoongi . aapney farmaya : ''apni nazar puri kar ley.'' usney kaha : maine nazar maani hai ke falan falan jagah janwer zibeh karun gi , jahan ke ehale-jahiliyat zibeh kiya kartey they. aapney puchha : ''kya wahan koi moorti thi jis ke liye wo zibeh kartey they?'' usney kaha : nahin. aapney puchha : ''to kya koi but tha jis ke liye zibeh kartey they?'' usney kaha : nahin. aapney farmaya : ''apni nazar puri kar ley.''"
3313,"Hazrat Sabit bin Zuhaak (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur main eik shakhs ne nazar maani ke wo maqame-bawaana par eik oont zibeh kerega . phir wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kaha : beshak maine bawaana mein oont zibeh kerney ki nazar maani hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne daryaft farmaya : ''kya wahan jahiliyat ka koi but tha jiski ibadat hoti rahi ho ?'' Sahaba ne kaha : nahin. aapney puchha : ''kya wo jagah unki mela gaah thi ?'' Sahaba ne kaha : nahin. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apni nazar puri kar ley , tehqiq aisi nazar ki koi wafaa nahin jis mein Allah ki nafarmani ho, aur na uski jo insan ki milkiyat mein na ho.''"
3314,"Hazrat Memuna binte Kardam (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke main apney walid ke sath hajj ke liye rawana hui jabke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hajj ke liye tashrif ley gaey they, to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki ziyaarat ki . maine logon ko suna, kehtey they ke ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hain. main aap ko khoob nazar bhar kar dekhti rahi. phir merey abba unke qarib huey jabkey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni oontni par Sawar they aur aap ke paas eik darra tha jaisey ke maktab ke muallim ke paas hota hai. maine badviyon ko aur logon ko suna jo keh rahey they ( الطبطبية , الطبطبية ( ) chaltey huey paon padney ki aawaz tibb tibb ya kodaa maarney ki aawaz.) merey abba aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qarib huey aur aap ke qadam pakad liye aur aap ki risaalat ka iqrar kiya aur aap ke paas khadey rahey aur aap ke irshaadaat suney aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine nazar maani hai ke agar merey yahan ladkey ki wiladat hui to main bawaana ke sirey par ghaati mein kaee bakriyan zibeh karunga . raawi kehta hai ghaaliban us ( Memuna ( ne pachas kahin . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne daryaft farmaya : ''kya wahan koi but tha? ''kaha nahin. aapney farmaya : ''jo to ne Allah ke liye nazar maani hai usey pura kar.'' chunanche merey abba ne bakriyon ko jama kya aur unhen zibeh kerney lagey to un mein se eik bakri bhag gaee to wo usey dhoondney nikley aur kehtey jatey they : ''aey Allah ! mujh se meri nazar puri kara dey.'' chunanche unhoney usey pa liya aur phir zibeh kar diya."
3315,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib ne Hazrat Memuna binte Kardam (Raziallahu anha) sey, usney apney walid se usi ki manind riwayat kiya. lekin qadrey ikhtisaar ke sath . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puchha : ''kya wahan koi but tha ya jahiliyat ka mela tha? ''kaha : kuchh bhi nahin. maine kaha : meri is walida ke zimmey nazar hai aur paidal chalna . kya main usey uski taraf se qaza ada karun? (aur alfaaz mein ibne Bashaar ( kya ham uski taraf se qaza ada keren? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan.''"
3316,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( ki azbaa oontni (pehley) bano Aqeel ke eik aadmi ke paas thi aur ye hajiyon ki sab sawaariyon se aagey rehti thi. chunanche wo aadmi qaid kar liya gaya aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke huzur pesh kiya gaya jabkey wo bandhaa hua tha aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney gadhey par they us par eik kapda dala gaya tha. usney kaha : aey Muhammad ! tum ne mujhey kyon pakda hai aur is oontni ko bhi jo hajiyon ki sawaariyon se aagey rehti hai? aapney farmaya : ''ham ne tujhey terey hulfa bano Saqeef ke jurm mein pakda hai.'' raawi ne kaha : bano Saqeef ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke do Sahaba ko qaid kar liya tha. is aadmi ne daurane guftgu ye bhi kaha : main musalman ho chuka ya kaha : maine Islam qubul kar liya hai. phir jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chal diye. . . . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : maine hadees ka ye hissey Muhammad bin Esa se samjha hai. . . us shakhs ne pukara aey Muhammad ! aey Muhammad ! aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bahut hi raheem aur naram dil they, to aap uski taraf mutawajjeh huey aur puchha : kya baat hai? usney kaha : beshak mein musalman hun. aapney farmaya : ''agar to ye baat us waqt kehta jab to apney maamley ka Malik tha to kamil taur par falah pa jata . . . .''Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : main phir Sulaiman ki riwayat ki taraf laut'taa hun. . . . us aadmi ne kaha : aey Muhammad ! main bhookaa hun mujhey khana khilao . main piyasa hun mujhey pani pilao . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(haan) ye teri hajat (bar-haq) hai.'' ya farmaya ''ye iski zarurat hai.'' garaz ye ke usey baad mein do aadmiyon ke fidye mein chhoda gaya. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne azbaa oontni ko apni sawari ke liye rok liya. raawi ne bayan kiya ke uskey baad mushrekin ne Madina ke bahir chartey janwaron par daaka dala aur azbaa oontni ko bhi ley gaey . jab wo usey ley gaey they to musalmanon ki eik aurat ko bhi qaid karkey ley gaey . wo log raat ke waqt apney oonton ko apney baadon mein chhod detey they. eik raat un par neend taari kar di gaee to wo aurat uthi (ke farar ho jaey) , to jis oont par bhi wo haath rakhti wo bilbilaaney lagta yahan tak ke azbaa oontni ke paas aai to goya eik naram khoo aur safar ki aadi oontni ke paas aa gaee (aur wo bilbilaai nahin) to wo us par Sawar ho gaee . phir usney apney liye ye nazar maani ke agar Allah ne usey najat de-di to wo is oontni ko bil-zaroor zibeh kar degi . chunanche jab wo Madina pahunchi to oontni pehchan li gaee ke ye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hai. isliye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko uski khabar di gaee to aapney usey bulwaya , usey laya gaya. aur uski nazar ke mutalliq bataya gaya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usney isey bahut bura badla diya. ya farmaya : ''tu ne isey bahut bura badla diya hai. Allah taala ne usey iskey zariey se najat di aur ye isey nahar kerney chali hai. jis kaam mein Allah ki gunah (nafarmaani) ho ya aisi chiz jis ka insan Malik na ho, us mein nazar nahin . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ye khatoon Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ki ehliya thi."
3317,"Janab Abdullah bin Kab jo apney walid ke na-bina ho janey ke baad unke qaaid hua kartey they. bayan kartey hain ke unkey walid ( Hazrat Kab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! meri tauba ka shukraana ye hai ke main Allah aur uskey Rasool ke liye apna maal sadqa kar dun aur is se dast-bardar ho jaun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apna kuchh maal apney paas rakho, ye tumharey liye behtar hai.'' to usney kaha : main apna wo hissey jo khaibar wala hai, apney paas rakhta hun."
3318,Janab Abdullah bin Kab bin Malik ne apney walid se riwayat kiya ke jab unki tauba qubul ho gaee to unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kiya ke main apney maal se dast bardar hota hun. aur mazkura baala hadees ki manind (خير لك) tak bayan kiya.
3319,"Hazrat Kab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke sahibzadey apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kaha, ya Abu-Lubaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne , ya kisi aur ne ke meri tauba ka shukraana ye hai ke main apna aabaai ghar jis mein mujh se ye gunah hua hai, chhod dun aur sadqa karkey apney sab maal se dast bardar ho jaun . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teesra hissey kafi hai.''"
3320,"Hazrat Kab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke sahibzadey ka bayan hai ke mazkura waqia Hazrat Abu-Lubaba ka hai aur uskey ham-maani bayan kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : isey Yunus ne b-waaste ibne-Shahab Zohri , bani Saaib bin Abi Lubaba ke kisi fard se aur aisey hi Zubaidi ne Zohri ke wastey , Husain bin Saaib bin Abi Lubaba se iskey misl (jasi) riwayat kiya hai."
3321,Janab Abdur-Rehman bin Abdullah bin Kab apney walid se wo dada usey apney qissey mein riwayat kartey hain ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! meri tauba ka Allah ke liye shukraana ye hai ke main apna sab maal Allah aur uskey Rasool ke liye sadqa kar dun . aapney farmaya : ''nahin.'' maine kaha : aadha maal . aapney farmaya : ''nahin.'' maine arz kiya : tihai maal . aapney farmaya : ''haan.'' to maine kaha : main apna khaibar wala hissey rakh leta hun.
3322,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney koi ghair tai-shuda nazar maani ho, uska kaffara qasam wala hai, aur jisney kisi gunah ke kaam ki nazar maan li ho to uska kaffara qasam wala hai, aur jisney koi aisi nazar maan li ho, jiski wo taqat na rakhta ho to uska kaffara qasam wala hai, aur jisney aisi nazar maani ho, jiski wo taqat rakhta ho to usey pura karey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : is hadees ko Wakee waghaira ne Abdullah bin Saeed bin Abi Hind se riwayat kartey huey Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) par moquf qarar diya hai."
3323,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nazar ka kaffara qasam wala hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : is riwayat ko Amr bin Haris ne bhi b-waaste Kab bin Alqama , ibne Shumasa se aur isney Hazrat Aqba se riwayat kiya hai."
3324,"Kab bin Alqama ne ibn Shumasa se suna, isney Abul-Khair se riwayat kiya, isney Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala hadees ki manind bayan kiya."
3325,Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine jahiliyat mein nazar maani thi ke masjide Haram main eik raat ke liye aetikaf karunga . to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''apni nazar puri karo.''
